 Rachel Reynolds<\/a> again. It&#8217;s one of the best we&#8217;ve done.<\/p>\n<p>&#8212;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hey! You can support us financially now &#8212; at no extra cost to you!<\/strong>\u00a0 It&#8217;s simple, really: \u00a0If you shop through Amazon.com by clicking on the widget to the right or the banner below:<\/p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" style=\"border: none;\" src=\"http:\/\/rcm.amazon.com\/e\/cm?t=hethsmyhu-20&amp;o=1&amp;p=12&amp;l=ur1&amp;category=amazonhomepage&amp;f=ifr\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p>&#8230; then, when you purchase something, we get a little taste of the action. <em>It&#8217;s that easy!<\/em><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Music Credits:<\/p>\n<p>Title Theme (Intro and Outtro): \u00a0 \u00a0<em>Perfect One<\/em>\u00a0(<a href=\"http:\/\/freemusicarchive.org\/music\/manbitesdog\/\" rel=\"cc:attributionURL\">Man Bites Dog<\/a>) \/\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/creativecommons.org\/licenses\/by-sa\/3.0\/\" rel=\"license\">CC BY-SA 3.0<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Interstitial Music: \u00a0<em>We&#8217;re in a Cloud, I&#8217;m Sure of It<\/em> (<a href=\"http:\/\/freemusicarchive.org\/music\/Father_Sleep\/\" rel=\"cc:attributionURL\">Father Sleep<\/a>) \/ <a href=\"http:\/\/creativecommons.org\/licenses\/by\/3.0\/us\/\" rel=\"license\">CC BY 3.0<\/a><\/p>\n<p>(If you&#8217;re interested in having your music featured on our podcast, please let us know!)<\/p>\n<div class=\"powerpress_player\" id=\"powerpress_player_3351\"><!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement('audio');<\/script><![endif]-->\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-662-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio\/mpeg\" src=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-050a.mp3?_=1\" \/><a href=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-050a.mp3\">http: